    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trolling Bowling is a cross between a realistic physics driven bowling game, and everything you were told to never do at a bowling alley. Bowl as normal, but hit the golden rings to earn trolling points. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175180/extras/ec6ffea6e46364a12fd931c2c933a194.poster.avif?t=1771937513\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175180/extras/ec6ffea6e46364a12fd931c2c933a194.webm?t=1771937513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175180/extras/ec6ffea6e46364a12fd931c2c933a194.mp4?t=1771937513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Trolling Powers</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your troll points to buy troll powers that hinder your opponents. Use a fog machine to blind them, cover the lane in landmines, or Set a Spring Trap to launch their ball.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175180/extras/11ab5fed9310a70ca86771575ddc347e.poster.avif?t=1771937513\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175180/extras/11ab5fed9310a70ca86771575ddc347e.webm?t=1771937513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175180/extras/11ab5fed9310a70ca86771575ddc347e.mp4?t=1771937513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Specialized Bowling Balls</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your troll points to purchase upgraded balls that help you counter the troll powers your opponents use on you. Did they turn your pins to concrete? Turn your ball into a grenade and blow right through!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175180/extras/58e5bf6be0aad750d3e3fbae724cdf3d.poster.avif?t=1771937513\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175180/extras/58e5bf6be0aad750d3e3fbae724cdf3d.webm?t=1771937513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175180/extras/58e5bf6be0aad750d3e3fbae724cdf3d.mp4?t=1771937513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Realistic pro-level lane oil patterns</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Practice mode to hone your skills countering troll powers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic bowling mode without troll powers or unrealistic balls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiplayer matches with up to 8 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many different whacky character models to choose from</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
